text: Eugen Albori Eugen Freiherr von Albori (or also known as Baron Eugen von Albori), (27 September 1838 – 4 September 1915) was an Austrian administrator. He served as the Austrian governor of Bosnia & Herzegovina between 1903 and 1907. == Notes == Category:1838 births Category:1915 deaths Category:Governors of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Barons of Austria Category:Grand Crosses of the Friedrich Order
